<section
  class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-32 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20"
>
  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-8 z-10">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-7xl leading-tight text-agujita-text">
      Costura creativa <br />
      <span class="text-agujita-primary italic">& piezas con alma</span>
    </h1>

    <p
      class="font-sans text-lg lg:text-xl text-agujita-text/80 max-w-md leading-relaxed"
    >
      Tu estilo, mi aguja. Diseños únicos y personalizables, hechos a mano en
      Barcelona con mucho mimo.
    </p>

    <div class="pt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/34610854434?text=¡Hola%20Gladys!%20Vengo%20de%20tu%20web%20y%20me%20gustaría%20hacerte%20una%20consulta..."
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="px-8 py-4 bg-agujita-text text-white rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-agujita-primary transition-colors shadow-lg cursor-pointer"
      >
        Hablemos de tu idea
      </a>
      <a
        href="#galeria"
        class="px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border border-agujita-text/20 text-agujita-text rounded-full font-medium hover:border-agujita-primary hover:text-agujita-primary transition-colors cursor-pointer"
      >
        Ver trabajos
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative">
    <div
      class="aspect-[4/5] bg-agujita-primary/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative border border-agujita-primary/5 group"
    >
      <img
        src="/img/hero.jpg"
        alt="Trabajo de costura creativa de Mi Agujita"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
      />
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 w-32 h-32 bg-agujita-primary/10 rounded-full blur-2xl -z-10"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-40 h-40 bg-agujita-bg rounded-full border border-agujita-primary/20 -z-10"
    >
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
